00:19:29.944 --> 00:19:35.316
You can teach your AI
assistant to help you include.

00:19:36.250 --> 00:19:41.355
In your prompt say,
write a plain language,

00:19:41.689 --> 00:19:44.625
use headings and bullets,

00:19:44.959 --> 00:19:48.696
propose alt text for images,
and avoid jargons.

00:19:49.730 --> 00:19:51.331
Then do a human review.

00:19:51.332 --> 00:19:56.637
AI is fast, but it doesn't know
your users like you do.

00:19:56.971 --> 00:19:58.030
Add a small link.

00:19:58.031 --> 00:19:59.372
Was this accessible for you?

00:19:59.373 --> 00:20:00.975
Invite feedback.

00:20:01.871 --> 00:20:05.145
Moreso, especially from people
using screen readers,

00:20:05.146 --> 00:20:09.516
captions and keyboard
only or high zoom,

00:20:09.717 --> 00:20:12.797
